TCAM recovery information
------------------------------
<field_enc>:
TCAM repair information is divided in groups of 16-bits (2 groups per 32-bit register)
              0..5: column
                 6: 0:core_a 1:core_b
             7..12: tcam index
            13..14: 0:super 1:es0 2:es2 3:ip6pfx
                15: 0:invalid group 1:valid group
